ot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;}}"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_row " data-bt-override-class="{}" data-structure="12"><div class="bt_bb_row_holder"><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate" data-width="12" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><div data-bb-version="4.9.1" class="bt_bb_latest_posts bt_bb_columns_3 bt_bb_gap_large bt_bb_image_shape_rounded"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/10546-2/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/iso-smart-globe-with-check-mark-guarantee-icons-on-2023-11-27-04-51-30-utc-640x427.jpg" alt="Introducing Responsible Giving: Unveiling Our Revolutionary Charity Assessment Platform!" title="Introducing Responsible Giving: Unveiling Our Revolutionary Charity Assessment Platform!" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/muslimgive-updates/" rel="category tag">MuslimGive Updates</a></li></ul></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_meta"><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_date">April 18, 2024</span><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_comments">0</span></div><h5 class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_title"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/10546-2/" target="_self">Introducing Responsible Giving: Unveiling Our Revolutionary Charity Assessment Platform!</a></h5><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_excerpt">March 26, 2024 We’re thrilled to announce the official launch of MuslimGive! MuslimGive is a first-of-its-kind Islamic Charity Assessment platform that will redefine how donors give. &nbsp; Empowering Informed Decisions* We understand that as a donor, you need clarity regarding the credibility and transparency of charitable organizations. We asked for your advice in our survey,...</div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/setting-a-standard-of-excellence-the-a-rated-by-muslimgive-badge/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Rating-badge-640x549.png" alt="Setting a Standard of Excellence: The ‘A Rated by MuslimGive’ Badge&nbsp;" title="Setting a Standard of Excellence: The ‘A Rated by MuslimGive’ Badge&nbsp;" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/muslimgive-updates/" rel="category tag">MuslimGive Updates</a></li></ul></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_meta"><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_date">April 17, 2024</span><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_comments">0</span></div><h5 class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_title"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/setting-a-standard-of-excellence-the-a-rated-by-muslimgive-badge/" target="_self">Setting a Standard of Excellence: The ‘A Rated by MuslimGive’ Badge&nbsp;</a></h5><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_excerpt">When it comes to charity, trust is paramount. When you donate, you want to be assured that your donation is being utilized with utmost integrity and reaching the cause you intended.&nbsp; This is where MuslimGive steps in. At the heart of MuslimGive’s mission lies the commitment to empower donors and charities with expert-led, thoroughly researched...</div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/march-milestones-progress-update-from-muslimgive/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MG-About-us-Page-640x718.jpg" alt="March Milestones: Progress Update from MuslimGive&nbsp;" title="March Milestones: Progress Update from MuslimGive&nbsp;" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/muslimgive-updates/" rel="category tag">MuslimGive Updates</a></li></ul></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_meta"><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_date">April 16, 2024</span><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_comments">0</span></div><h5 class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_title"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/march-milestones-progress-update-from-muslimgive/" target="_self">March Milestones: Progress Update from MuslimGive&nbsp;</a></h5><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_excerpt">18 Canadian Charity Ratings Published and Counting!&nbsp; &nbsp; A journey that started in 2023, our vision is to empower Muslim donors with expert-led, meticulously researched Charity Assessments for every Islamic charitable organization. Our mission is simple: we research on behalf of donors to support your Zakat &amp; Sadaqah giving decisions&nbsp; We believe that by providing...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-bb-version="4.9.1" class="bt_bb_row " style="display:none;" data-bt-override-class="{}" data-structure="12"><div class="bt_bb_row_holder"><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_center bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in bt_bb_animation_move_down animate" data-width="12" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_top_spacing_small bt_bb_bottom_spacing_normal" data-bt-override-class="null"></div><div class="bt_bb_button bt_bb_color_scheme_6 bt_bb_icon_position_left bt_bb_style_filled bt_bb_width_inline bt_bb_shape_inherit bt_bb_target_self bt_bb_text_transform_inherit bt_bb_size_normal bt_bb_align_inherit" style="; --primary-color:#ffffff; --secondary-color:#1f3181;" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_size_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_size_normal&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;},&quot;bt_bb_align_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_align_inherit&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;}}"><a href="/blog/" target="_self" class="bt_bb_link" title="Read more in the blog"><span class="bt_bb_button_text">Read more in the blog</span><span data-ico-fontawesome="" class="bt_bb_icon_holder"></span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!-- cell_inner --></div><!-- cell --></div><!-- port --></section><section data-bb-version="4.8.8" id="bt_bb_section6731d106144e2" class="bt_bb_section bt_bb_layout_boxed_1200 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_top_spacing_normal bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_top_spacing_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_top_spacing_normal&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;},&quot;bt_bb_bottom_spacing_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;}}"><div class="bt_bb_port"><div class="bt_bb_cell"><div class="bt_bb_cell_inner"><div class="bt_bb_row " data-bt-override-class="{}" data-structure="12"><div class="bt_bb_row_holder"><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_center bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate" data-width="12" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><header class="bt_bb_headline bt_bb_font_weight_normal bt_bb_subheadline_text_transform_default bt_bb_dash_bottom bt_bb_size_extralarge bt_bb_align_inherit" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_size_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_size_extralarge&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;extralarge&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;extralarge&quot;},&quot;bt_bb_align_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_align_inherit&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;}}"><h2 class="bt_bb_headline_tag"><span class="bt_bb_headline_content"><span>Latest Articles from <b>MuslimGive</b></span></span></h2></header><div data-bb-version="4.8.0" class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_top_spacing_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_top_spacing_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_top_spacing_none&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;none&quot;},&quot;bt_bb_bottom_spacing_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium&quot;,&quot;xxl&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;}}"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_row " data-bt-override-class="{}" data-structure="12"><div class="bt_bb_row_holder"><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate" data-width="12" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><div data-bb-version="4.9.1" class="bt_bb_latest_posts bt_bb_columns_3 bt_bb_gap_large bt_bb_image_shape_rounded"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/transparency-2/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/close-up-of-business-graph-analysis-document-2023-11-27-05-37-06-utc-1-640x427.jpg" alt="Empowering Trust in Muslim Charities – MuslimGive’s Groundbreaking Findings" title="Empowering Trust in Muslim Charities – MuslimGive’s Groundbreaking Findings" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/featured/" rel="category tag">Featured</a></li></ul></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_meta"><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_date">October 14, 2024</span><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_comments">0</span></div><h5 class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_title"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/transparency-2/" target="_self">Empowering Trust in Muslim Charities – MuslimGive’s Groundbreaking Findings</a></h5><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_excerpt">Did you know the global Muslim Ummah donates nearly 1 trillion dollars each year? That’s a staggering amount of generosity, but how can you be sure your Zakat and Sadaqah are being handled with the trust and transparency they deserve? At MuslimGive, our mission is to ensure that your charitable donations are managed with the...</div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/transparency/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/transparency-640x640.png" alt="Why Transparency is Crucial: The Risks of Blind Giving" title="Why Transparency is Crucial: The Risks of Blind Giving" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/featured/" rel="category tag">Featured</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_meta"><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_date">July 31, 2024</span><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_comments">0</span></div><h5 class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_title"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/transparency/" target="_self">Why Transparency is Crucial: The Risks of Blind Giving</a></h5><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_excerpt">Imagine donating $100 to feed a needy family nutritious hot meals, only to find out your contribution barely provides them with a basic, far from nutritious meal. This could be the reality when charities lack transparency in the management and allocation of your donations.&nbsp; Donating without due diligence can have serious repercussions. When donors give...</div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/why-you-should-donate-to-registered-charities/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/registered.png" alt="Why You Should Donate to Registered Charities" title="Why You Should Donate to Registered Charities" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/featured/" rel="category tag">Featured</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a></li>
                                                                            <li><a href="https://muslimgive.org/category/blog/" rel="category tag">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_meta"><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_date">June 10, 2024</span><span class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_comments">0</span></div><h5 class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_title"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/why-you-should-donate-to-registered-charities/" target="_self">Why You Should Donate to Registered Charities</a></h5><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_excerpt">Charity Status: A Critical Component of Due Diligence How can you be assured that your charity is monitored and regulated, reducing the risk of your Zakat and Sadaqah being mismanaged?&nbsp; &nbsp; One of the core areas of MuslimGive’s assessment is the charity’s registration status. Charities must be registered with the appropriate government agencies to operate...</div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_image"><a href="https://muslimgive.org/your-zakat-responsibility/" target="_self"><img src="https://muslimgive.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/zakat-2023-11-27-05-08-19-utc-640x427.jpg" alt="Your Zakat, Your Responsibility" title="Your Zakat, Your Responsibility" loading="lazy" "=""></a></div><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_content"><div class="bt_bb_latest_posts_item_category"><ul class="post-categories">
